To use this yourself, assuming a standard Vim install:

    { cd "$HOME" &&
      mkdir vimbak &&
      mv .vim{,rc} vimbak &&
      git clone https://github.com/mrdomino/vim .vim &&
      ln -s .vim/vimrc .vimrc
    }

Make sure ~/tmp exists, or remove the line in .vimrc that sets it as the swap
dir.
